<subSubSection id="5CBC65591871FFE7FF65FBCB4D70F946" pageId="6" pageNumber="492" type="description">
<paragraph id="141936D21871FFE7FF65FBCB498FFBA3" blockId="6.[151,1437,1116,1897]" box="[151,436,1116,1141]" pageId="6" pageNumber="492">Uniformly creamy white.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="141936D21871FFE7FF35FB174AE6FAD2" blockId="6.[151,1437,1116,1897]" pageId="6" pageNumber="492">
Crown depressed in middle with one median carina, anterior margin without rim, surface smooth and shining, posterior margin of crown reflexed, keeled; lateral margin keeled and reflexed in basal half and apical half raised and rounded. Lateral margin of pronotum slightly concave laterally. Forewings in both sexes without lateral small subapical cell present in other species of 
<taxonomicName id="D3A64D511871FFE7FD90FB7A4AEDFAD2" box="[610,726,1261,1284]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Signoretia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="492" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="26D2EAC01871FFE7FD90FB7A4AEDFAD2" box="[610,726,1261,1284]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="492">Signoretia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="141936D21871FFE7FF35FA874D41F99E" blockId="6.[151,1437,1116,1897]" pageId="6" pageNumber="492">
<emphasis id="26D2EAC01871FFE7FF35FA874954FAFE" box="[199,367,1296,1320]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="492">Male genitalia</emphasis>
. Pygofer with dorsal margin straight, posterodorsal angle almost rectangular, ventral margin straight, ventral process stouter, exceeding height of pygofer, apex slightly curved anteriorly, body of process with several short microsetae. Subgenital plate rather triangular with posterior apex bluntly angled, long hair like setae on outer margin and series of smaller microsetae along submargin of entire length, plate approximately three times as long as wide at base. Connective Y-shaped, arms short. Style without subapical lobe, distal 0.33 curved laterally with lateral margin toothed. Aedeagus membranous, atrium elongate, with pair of slender processes ventrad of shaft directed posteriorly, shaft cylindrical, short, in dorsal view oppressed, subequal to ventral process, gonopore apical, ventral process elongated, each arm of ventral process crossing over each other at base, with dorsal marginal brush like setae on inner margin and without setae on outer margin. Segment X elongate without any processes.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="141936D21871FFE7FF35F9C34D70F946" blockId="6.[151,1437,1116,1897]" pageId="6" pageNumber="492">
<emphasis id="26D2EAC01871FFE7FF35F9C34946F9BB" bold="true" box="[199,381,1620,1645]" pageId="6" pageNumber="492">Measurements.</emphasis>
Male 
<quantity id="D35E9B371871FFE7FE20F9C34A14F9BA" box="[466,559,1620,1645]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="6.7" pageId="6" pageNumber="492" unit="mm" value="6.7">6.7 mm</quantity>
long, 
<quantity id="D35E9B371871FFE7FD71F9C24AE4F9BA" box="[643,735,1621,1645]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.4" pageId="6" pageNumber="492" unit="mm" value="1.4">1.4 mm</quantity>
wide across eyes and also across posterolateral angles of pronotum. Female 
<quantity id="D35E9B371871FFE7FE99F9EF49FAF946" box="[363,449,1656,1680]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="7.2" pageId="6" pageNumber="492" unit="mm" value="7.2">7.2 mm</quantity>
long, 
<quantity id="D35E9B371871FFE7FDF5F9EF4A66F946" box="[519,605,1656,1681]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.5" pageId="6" pageNumber="492" unit="mm" value="1.5">1.5 mm</quantity>
wide across eyes ad also across posterolateral angles of pronotum.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
